snippet.textDisplay: I have to say that personally I never jumped on the train when it came to taking the time to get to know celebrities or their backgrounds. I just used to believe it was just not worth worrying about, but then my little brother introduced me to Hot Ones. I've learned so much about the guests and now earnestly watch their collective careers more closely because of what I learned about them on this show. I love the style of the interviews almost as much as I love how intimate the setting is. You break down these people from icons back to human  beings and I find myself relating to some of them when I never thought I would. Thank you so much for 10 PHENOMENAL seasons! Thanks for all your hard work to entertain us and may 2020 bring you so much more!! (also, if HO did in fact host presidential candidates I would actually watch the campaign js)
